  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates that TRPV1 receptors play a complex role in pelvic organ cross-sensitization, with RTX treatment showing both beneficial effects (reduced neuronal excitability) and potential limitations (enhanced somatic field responses).",
    "The temporal aspect is important - RTX effects were only observed during acute inflammation, not during resolved colitis."
  ]
